            span.
        #navbarNav.offcanvas.offcanvas-end(tabindex='-1'): .offcanvas-body
            ul.navbar-nav.link-box.me-auto
                li.nav-item: a.nav-link(href='/'+lang+'/about') 鏡子線上展
                li.nav-item.dropdown
                    a.nav-link#artistDropdownMenuLink(href='#' data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false") 藝術家
                    ul.dropdown-menu(aria-labelledby="artistDropdownMenuLink")
                        li
                            a.dropdown-item(href='/'+lang+'/artist/1') 王筱璦‧王筱璦金工藝術
                            a.dropdown-item(href='/'+lang+'/artist/2') 潘子村‧村 碟樂
                            a.dropdown-item(href='/'+lang+'/artist/3') 黃虹毓‧土星工作室
                            a.dropdown-item(href='/'+lang+'/artist/4') 陳向榮‧向榮水果行
                            a.dropdown-item(href='/'+lang+'/artist/5') 康雅筑‧織物地圖
                            a.dropdown-item(href='/'+lang+'/artist/6') 林秀蘋(思良)‧BONTE好物金工
                            a.dropdown-item(href='/'+lang+'/artist/7') 張博傑‧真真鑲嵌玻璃研究所
                            a.dropdown-item(href='/'+lang+'/artist/8') 賴信佑‧光山行漆器工藝
                li.nav-item: a.nav-link(href='/'+lang+'/more') 了解更多
            ul.navbar-nav.link-box.flex-row
                li.nav-item: a.ms-3.btn.btn-purple(href='https://player.soundon.fm/p/25079601-f138-48b3-868b-9e2be7886ca7' target="_blank") 🎧閉上眼聽展覽
                li.nav-item: a.ms-4.btn.btn-purple(href='#' data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#helpModal") 🦄
                li.nav-item.dropdown
                    a.ms-4.btn.btn-purple#langDropdownLink(href='#' data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false") 🌍
                    ul.dropdown-menu.lang-dropdown(aria-labelledby="langDropdownLink")
                        li
                            a.dropdown-item(href='#' data-lang-target="/zh_tw") 中文
                            a.dropdown-item(href='#' data-lang-target="/en") ENGLISH
